How to Bookmark to iPhone

  1. Tap the Share icon
  2. Scroll down and tap "Add to Home Screen"
  3. Tap Add to save to your Home Screen

How to Bookmark to iPad

  1. Tap "Add to Home Screen"
  2. Tap "Add" to complete adding the icon to the Home screen

How to Bookmark to Android Phone

  1. Tap the Create Bookmark icon
  2. Tap on the drop-down menu
  3. Tap "Home Screen"

How to Bookmark to Android Tablet

  1. Tap the Create Bookmark icon
  2. Tap on the drop-down menu
  3. Tap "Home Screen"
